  "texts": [
    "We used a similar process to create a new dataset for Spanish without the use of dictionaries.",
    "Because the CRAFT dataset is preformatted in the CONLL format, we reconstructed all of the words with an \"O\" tag to make real sentences, as well as multi-word NEs.",
    "We fed Google Translate with the sentences separated from the NEs, either single words or multi-words.",
    "Then, we mapped back the tags to avoid errors in the misalignment of sentences.",
    "The translation process of this dataset is described as follows:"
